<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maintenance — iTransport</title>
    <style>
        :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0; min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #f8fafc; color: #0f172a; padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        .card {
            max-width: 460px; width: 100%; text-align: center;
            background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(2,6,23,.08);
        }
        .icon {
            width: 64px; height: 64px; margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 9999px; background: #fff7ed; color: #ea580c; font-size: 30px;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-weight: 600; }
        p { margin: 0 0 .75rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.55; font-size: .95rem; }
        .msg {
            margin-top: 1rem; padding: .75rem 1rem; border-radius: 10px;
            background: #f1f5f9; color: #334155; font-size: .9rem; white-space: pre-wrap;
        }
        .logout { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: .85rem; color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; }
        .logout:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body { background: #0b1120; color: #e2e8f0; }
            .card { background: #0f172a; border-color: #1e293b; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4); }
            .icon { background: #431407; color: #fb923c; }
            p { color: #94a3b8; }
            .msg { background: #172033; color: #cbd5e1; }
            .logout { color: #94a3b8; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🛠️</div>
        <h1>Application en maintenance</h1>
        <p>L'application est momentanément indisponible pour maintenance. Merci de réessayer dans quelques instants.</p>
        {% if message %}<div class="msg">{{ message }}</div>{% endif %}
        <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}" class="logout">Se déconnecter</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
